### **3. 2_LogScannerLite**  
**Description:**  
A minimalistic tool to scan logs and detect repeating issues and warning spikes.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# LogScannerLite - Fast Log Inspection

LogScannerLite helps developers quickly find error patterns in log files using simple text analysis.

## Features
- Highlights most frequent lines  
- Quick keyword search  
- Works with any plain-text log  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/2_LogScannerLite.git
cd 2_LogScannerLite
python analyze.py log.txt
